data.description: What a great find! This home is ready for a new family. So much room and storage you will be amazed! This family home has an open plan living area. Lovely kitchen with newer appliances, cabinets galore. Large dining area with custom built cabinets for all of your special items.  The den area has a brick fireplace to keep you cozy warm in the winter time. Custom built books shelves. Beautiful hardwood floors in living room and bedrooms. With the open plan of this home you can arrange and use your space in many different ways that suit you.  The master bedroom is a great size with private bathroom.  The bathroom is handicapped accessible also. Large glassed porch, great for extra room, sun room, game room, you name it. Fill it with plants and it will be beautiful.  Super nice carport. Ramp to enter home if handicapped, easy entry. Detached workshop.  Much to enjoy with this property.    Only minutes to town.   Model School district.
